Hello all,

In case you were not able to attend GECCO, we have videos of th=
ree of the Evolving AI Lab talks.

You can view them at the (brand new!) Ev=
olving AI Lab website. 

Encouraging creative thinking in robots improves t=
heir ability to solve challenging problems: http://www.evolvingai.org/node/=
29

Novelty Search Creates Robots with General Skills for Exploration: http=
://www.evolvingai.org/node/31

Evolving Neural Networks That Are Both Modul=
ar and Regular: HyperNeat Plus the Connection Cost Technique: http://www.ev=
olvingai.org/node/30

PS. Please let us know what you think of the website =
and, especially, if you notice anything wrong with it that we need to fix. =




Best regards,
Jeff Clune

Assistant Professor
Computer Science
